OL,3,CTwo-thirds of private tenants worried
OL,4,Cabout paying their rent ` Big Issue
OL,6,FTwo-thirds of people living in private
OL,7,Frented accommodation are worried about
OL,8,Fpaying their rent, research suggests.
OL,10,FThe Big Issue magazine said its study
OL,11,Frevealed a "troubling picture" of
OL,12,Fhousing vulnerability.
OL,14,FThe poll of 2,000 adults showed that
OL,15,Fone in two felt an increased risk of
OL,16,Fhomelessness compared with last year.
OL,18,FAlongside the research, the Big Issue
OL,19,Flaunched a new film, The 12 Days of
OL,20,FHomelessness, highlighting the leading
OL,21,Fcauses of homelessness across the UK.
